body:
Hello there,


to start with, my name is Lukas, i am 15 years old and i was born in Austria (not Australia) and I would like to search for a team, that wants to improve its rank and its skill to get better. While I am despairing to get out of Bronze V Solo/Duo Q, i thought " hey, why not search for a team to rank up in Flex Q". So that's the reason, why i am searching on this Forum for teammates. If you've decided to take me into your team, just add "TukmasterLP10" to League and write to that topic. Now, I'll {{summoner:4}} out of here and i hope, I'll find some new friends here ^^
